text:
Terry Crews' 90 day 'sex fast' helped bring him closer to wife 
Fox News Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Terry Crews credits abstaining from sex for 90 days with helping him reconnect with his wife, Rebecca Crews. 
"Ninety days -- no sex, all relationship, all talk, all cuddled," he candidly...
